data.text:
He's a Rocketman! Tom Hardy to Play Elton John in Biopic

Tom Hardy will star as Elton John in the upcoming biopic Rocketman, Deadline reports. The film will chronicle the life and epic career of the singer known for "Rocket Man," "Candle in the Wind," "Your Song," "Bennie and the Jets" and a slew of other hits. John...

Top Videos: Lena Dunham, Screaming Goats and a Rubik's Cube

Check out our favorite video clips of the week: Screaming goats: Goats are so hot right now. Here are our two favorite mashups featuring that disturbing clip of a goat "screaming": Miley Cyrus' "Party in the USA" and Taylor Swift's "I Knew You Were a Goat When You Walked In." Check out a host of other goat remixes here. 

Top Videos of the Week: Best of Liz & Dick, Jimmy Fallon and Rashida Jones' Holiday Song

'Tis the season to get into the holiday spirit — and this week, Jimmy Fallon and Rashida Jones helped viewers do just that, with a holiday medley set to the most popular songs of the year. Meanwhile, some pranksters decided to play a practical joke on Black Friday shoppers by dressing up as Target employees and giving the customers some (misguided) information about the store's deals. Check out those clips in our Top Videos of the Week, as well as a terrifying Brazilian hidden camera stunt, an Inception­-inspired parody of 7th Heaven's marijuana episode, the best of Liz & Dick, and more.

Exclusive Videos: The Simpsons Spoofs Inception For Fox's Blockbuster Movie Night

If you've ever envisioned a Family Guy/Friday The 13th mash-up (and, really, who hasn't?), you're in luck. This Sunday, all five of Fox's animated comedies — The Cleveland Show, The Simpsons, Bob's Burgers, Family Guy and American Dad — will air special blockbuster-themed episodes.
